Privacy Policy for Prayer Time App

Effective Date: [Insert Date]

Thank you for choosing Prayer Time, a mobile application that provides users with accurate prayer times without the need for account creation. Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.

1. Information We Collect:
1.1 Prayer Times Data:

The app retrieves and displays prayer times based on your location. No personal information is stored or transmitted in this process.
1.2 Usage Data:

We may collect anonymous usage data, such as app opens, interactions, and feature usage, to improve the app's performance and user experience. This data is collected in aggregate and cannot be used to identify individual users.
2. Location Information:
2.1 Geolocation:

The app uses your device's geolocation data to determine your location and provide accurate prayer times. This information is processed locally on your device and is not stored or transmitted to our servers.
3. Data Security:
3.1 Storage:

Prayer Time app does not store any personal information, including your location data or prayer times, on our servers. All information is processed locally on your device.
3.2 Security Measures:

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect the app from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of your data.
4. Third-Party Services:
4.1 Location Services:

The app may use third-party location services to enhance the accuracy of prayer times. Please review the privacy policies of these services for information on how they handle your data.
5. Children's Privacy:
The Prayer Time app is not intended for children under the age of 4+. We do not knowingly collect or process personal information from individuals under 13 years of age.
6. Changes to Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices. Users will be notified of any significant changes via the app or our website.
7. Contact Us:
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your privacy or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [your@email.com].
By using the Prayer Time app, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Please read this policy carefully and check for updates periodically.

Thank you for trusting us with your privacy.
